OL,2,MChasing Eclipses throughout the Cosmos
OL,4,CAffelia Wibisono
OL,5,CSat 10:00-10:30
OL,6,CStage C
OL,8,GSolar eclipses are one of the most
OL,9,Gmagnificent sights on Earth. Whether
OL,10,Git’s the spine-tingling midday
OL,11,Gtwilight during a total solar eclipse,
OL,12,Gor watching the Moon taking a “giant
OL,13,Gbite” out of the Sun during a partial
OL,14,Gevent (like the one we’ll experience
OL,15,Gin August 2026!), these alignments
OL,16,Ghave captivated people for millennia.
OL,17,GBut what about eclipses beyond the
OL,18,GEarth? Recently, The Artemis 2 crew
OL,19,Gexperienced something no other human
OL,20,Gbeings have - an hour long total solar
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
